{"tid":2098431,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[貼紙師入] 如何令藍絲一張貼紙都搣唔到","createTime":"2020-07-07T13:03:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-08T04:25:29.000Z","uid":240369,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f4c849159ef09dd0bd9d760113730cdade71ce32","tid":2098431,"uid":240369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T13:03:58.000Z","msg":"［借account轉貼］<br />\n<br />\n//眼見手足痴個啲貼紙成日俾藍絲搣左，如果文宣痴左一日就俾人搣走左，印刷錢同冒既險都哂左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">點樣可以令藍絲一張都搣唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n(只限小至中型貼紙 痴A4咁大張你好易俾人捉)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n試諗下，藍絲見到搣唔到既原因不外乎有兩個<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">（1）佢接觸唔到張貼紙</span></span><br />\n<br />\n張貼紙俾人睇到就有效果，唔需要條友掂到。嚟啲地方搭程巴士望出𥦬就有一大堆：<span style=\"color: orange;\">郵筒頂，巴士外身， 巴士坐位側邊.....</span>想像下，廢老搭巴士個陣見到隔離巴士痴左「光時」，佢可以做啲咩？落車去對面巴士搣？定扑爆玻璃去搣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><br />\n一句記之曰：見到既搣唔到，搣到既見唔到，玻璃係你好幫手</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">（2）佢唔夠時間搣/情況唔許可搣</span></span><br />\n<br />\n貼紙師同撕紙狗比，前者其實係有先天優勢。貼張迷你文宣兩秒都唔洗，撕紙狗呢？分分鐘要佢企定定係度搣成分鐘。我地就係要運用優勢，痴係啲藍絲唔可以企定定搣既地方，迫佢地望完就算。嚟啲地方都係周街都有，例如<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">電梯，地鐵車廂門外面，上落車位</span>....當架地鐵或者巴士嚟度個陣，藍絲會選擇冒住俾乘客司機屌既風險撕紙定就咁上車？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />電梯不斷郁，藍絲點企係度搣紙？地鐵車廂門更加係曝光率超高包保勁多人見到，但俾人撕到既可能性近符零，除非條友想俾架野拖行。相反，上到車企係門邊捱玻璃，隊隻手去道門度貼，兩秒就搞掂。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n只要用嚟兩個原則貼文宣，基本上藍絲一張都唔會搣到。如果有埋反面貼紙痴個面有字，咁就無敵了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好再痴係啲俾人秒搣既地方啦手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>//<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">屌我係藍絲 網上見到嚟篇文真係勁嬲!!!! 班黃屍竟然諗啲咁既方法等我地撕唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我要貼上嚟大力譴責 你地千奇唔好咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果唔係我就舉報你地班仆街!!!!!</span></span>"},{"pid":"d876aa83c9021b280f7d230b5ac13d0a6b602c6f","tid":2098431,"uid":277659,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T13:07:47.000Z","msg":"地鐵車廂門外既話車站會有CCTV<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e31f09bb8bd0f282b380af411687c2283bd104e","tid":2098431,"uid":240369,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d876aa83c9021b280f7d230b5ac13d0a6b602c6f","tid":2098431,"uid":277659,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T13:07:47.000Z","msg":"地鐵車廂門外既話車站會有CCTV<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T13:26:44.000Z","msg":"影到你隻手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48b2dd01fb17c64a5dfc9011ff9b83076a742bea","tid":2098431,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T13:58:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img s